ary, but repeatedly fails to establish the **credibility** requirement. The characterization as \"claimed/joked,\" \"vague,\" and the missing primary source mean the evidence does not preponderate toward a credible qualifying announcement.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e858fdfc00c54b2fa88ece77","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"not_demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\""},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"not_demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782803588186,"responseId":"gen-1782803588-Iw9sYOXoSdncw9cOR74P","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-20260216"}}
